{
  "stem": "17135.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was-- the, the the second in command was the Lagerschreiber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Schreiber means the official, like a bureaucrat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was the second in command because he had control of all the, the, the registers, the names, who worked here, who were there, who worked well, who worked bad, and, and the names.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had a very responsible job there in, in--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, they call it in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was actually in charge of all the registry, the inside registry of all the documentation they have who is there, who died, and who is sick, who was deported, who was transferred.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was his job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very responsible job as far as the SS is concerned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They want to know at all times what is going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They want to know at all times that everybody is there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they have to have confidence in him that he is not hiding something, is not swindling because, otherwise, people could escape, and they would never know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they had strict control over the registration, over all the documentation about who is there, and where they-- in which block they are, how old they are, where they work, and what have you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He took over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And since I was already there, he kept me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, I started working for the underground, mainly because just listening to the conversation that they had, and he constantly had SS men, SS-- Scharfuhrer, Oberscharfuhrer, Hauptscharfuhrer, they came to him because when they wanted to implement something in the camp, they had to go to him, to the Lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He made things happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "An SS, for example, who wanted to have a special selection, a special that, a special this, he went to the Lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
